Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.79,0:11:47.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,0)\pos(620,633)}尔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.79,0:11:47.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,0)\pos(673,633)}杰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.83,0:11:47.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,0)\pos(725,633)}夫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.64,0:11:45.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.92,0:11:46.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.43,0:12:05.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们两个的emphatier等级无法稳定在规定值？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.67,0:12:09.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说 迪奥君和弗洛姆无法进行联结？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.99,0:12:11.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都不被允许呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.72,0:12:12.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.07,0:12:14.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在莱克路易斯的测试中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.79,0:12:18.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和弗洛姆应该显示出了良好联结反应
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.43,0:12:22.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在联结者候补生之中也是最好的相性呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.51,0:12:27.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪奥 你的emphatier波形跟以前相比有所变化
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.39,0:12:29.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的波形变了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.38,0:12:30.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.20,0:12:32.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始偏离基准波形了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.62,0:12:33.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.07,0:12:34.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原因是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.34,0:12:37.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在还不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.17,0:12:40.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说是因为有实战经验了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.35,0:12:42.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种可能性无法否定呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.55,0:12:45.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样都好啦 摄影怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.25,0:12:47.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 我有一个提议
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.18,0:12:48.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.52,0:12:51.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从新人演员摇身一变
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.06,0:12:55.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变成摄影的了 有大出息了啊 小子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.02,0:12:57.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连你也这么说啊 唐先生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.02,0:13:00.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡濑少尉 请马上到检查室来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.79,0:13:02.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重复一遍 渡濑少尉…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.52,0:13:16.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.67,0:13:19.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厉害 这个数值是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.56,0:13:23.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次联结测试 就如此匹配
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.89,0:13:27.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样 可以 还是不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.06,0:13:28.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾维拉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.19,0:13:31.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,数值上没有任何问题
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.56,0:13:34.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,允许
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.69,0:13:38.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 驾驶舱内的画面之后再替换成迪奥君的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.09,0:13:41.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗洛姆就和青叶君联结
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.69,0:13:43.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.15,0:13:44.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.32,0:13:47.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多指教？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.99,0:13:48.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.48,0:13:58.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各valiancer现在开始的起飞是宣传任务
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.40,0:14:00.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重复一遍 宣传任务
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.03,0:14:06.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外 由于交换了联结者 部分搭乘者有所变更
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.47,0:14:08.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,LUXON是渡濑青叶少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.00,0:14:09.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.90,0:14:12.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,BRADYON迪奥·韦恩伯格少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.07,0:14:14.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变更为弗洛姆·梵塔雷少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.97,0:14:18.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说是第一次当同伴 也不用客气哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.21,0:14:19.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 包在我身上了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.11,0:14:23.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外 韦恩伯格少尉搭乘BERYL
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.06,0:14:27.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实战经验吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.28,0:14:31.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然会影响emphatier波形 这不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.01,0:14:33.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么为什么只有我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.93,0:14:36.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打起精神来 迪奥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.10,0:14:38.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也会有这样的日子啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.60,0:14:41.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 没必要在意 摄影负责人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.78,0:14:43.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要得意忘形了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.83,0:14:49.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错不错 LUXON
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.06,0:14:52.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就期待能拍出好画面了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.09,0:15:06.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就开始吧 青叶君
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.11,0:15:07.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.13,0:15:10.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连接弗洛姆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.95,0:15:11.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接受
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.51,0:15:21.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个比青叶同学和迪奥第一次联结的时候还…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.29,0:15:23.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.68,0:15:48.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青叶君真的很厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.44,0:15:52.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有接受联结训练过程就能做到那样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.00,0:16:01.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好快的速度
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.04,0:16:13.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是和我的话 说不定还是偶然
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.32,0:16:17.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 没想到和弗洛姆还是第一次见面…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.76,0:16:18.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.86,0:16:24.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中断
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.42,0:16:32.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能还会继续 对象valiancer
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.12,0:16:35.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让杜兰中尉立刻起飞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.24,0:16:35.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.91,0:16:37.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是千岁的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.46,0:16:39.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有部队进发的征兆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.18,0:16:41.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 究竟是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.69,0:16:44.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,BERYL E的影像传过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.06,0:16:45.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个机体是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.49,0:16:54.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是让我们亲卫师团特意前来的新型机吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.86,0:16:56.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按计划进行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.52,0:16:57.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把天鹅吸引过来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.35,0:16:59.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.27,0:17:06.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心  这是从佐基利亚本部来的精英部队
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.68,0:17:07.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.76,0:17:11.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来是认真想要把联结系统击溃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.89,0:17:20.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 竟然要用BERYL和这些家伙做对手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.41,0:17:27.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是亲卫军吗 终于开始盯上我们了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.97,0:17:29.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饶了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.16,0:17:33.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.68,0:17:47.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会让你逃走的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.93,0:17:49.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.07,0:17:54.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对第一次的联结来说果然还是未尽人意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.10,0:17:57.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们两个的emphatier等级非常厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.87,0:18:01.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此苦战 就说明对方很厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.92,0:18:11.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 不愧是亲卫军 毫无破绽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.67,0:18:21.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是浮游机雷吗 路线是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.99,0:18:25.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能行动自如
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.96,0:18:29.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 出不来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.91,0:18:31.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.85,0:18:35.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.37,0:18:38.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要趁着这个气势突破的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.53,0:18:49.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说 把LUXON逼入绝境了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.73,0:18:51.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能过去支援
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.00,0:18:55.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青叶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.04,0:18:59.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.09,0:19:01.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,微不足道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.40,0:19:10.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为只有速度和机动性就能赢得了我们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.11,0:19:13.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是想把他引入大炮的射线内吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.20,0:19:16.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会让你得手的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.34,0:19:24.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.87,0:19:37.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.48,0:19:52.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,区区联合的量产机
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.43,0:19:53.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要追吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.65,0:19:58.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包围阵型已经崩坏 需要重新拟定策略
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.10,0:20:03.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,威胁 撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.80,0:20:09.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 拍到了最棒的画面 最棒了 最棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.91,0:20:11.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们还会回来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.95,0:20:14.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我会严密戒备的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.99,0:20:27.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驾驶BERYL还能那么活跃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.52,0:20:28.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.16,0:20:31.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢啦 得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.37,0:20:33.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你果然很厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.56,0:20:35.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这是任务
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.92,0:20:38.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.97,0:20:43.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然没有比关系生死的战斗更有震撼力的画面了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.48,0:20:45.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此 这是最后的拍摄
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.78,0:20:55.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 准备好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.99,0:20:57.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正式开始了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.21,0:20:59.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.18,0:21:00.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.17,0:21:01.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.64,0:21:06.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 你也和我们一起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.27,0:21:08.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's  联结
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.27,0:21:08.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(706,658)}coupling
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.79,0:21:11.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 OK
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.23,0:21:12.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两位都辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.17,0:21:14.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.89,0:21:15.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拍摄高度也OK？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.45,0:21:18.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么回去以后就马上编辑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.73,0:21:23.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,补给整备完毕之后
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.55,0:21:25.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就马上再次出击
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.35,0:21:27.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要给他们休息的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.63,0:21:28.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.68,0:21:33.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此 难怪阿尔弗里德·加兰特会感到棘手了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.13,0:21:36.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是下次不会再这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.90,0:21:41.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联合的新型机 我已经看透了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.41,0:21:43.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.42,0:21:46.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也能做出那种表情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.07,0:21:47.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你指什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.23,0:21:49.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's  联结
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.23,0:21:49.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(708,660)}coupling
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.53,0:21:52.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为那是任务
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.44,0:21:55.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是个不错的家伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.82,0:21:58.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再多待一会就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.54,0:21:59.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.33,0:22:01.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这么说啊 迪奥
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.63,0:22:05.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 摄影组的各位刚才已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.47,0:22:10.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗洛姆 就这样分配进Cygnus是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.91,0:22:14.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 我没说吗
